1
00:01:53,033 --> 00:01:58,200
(The All-devouring Whale: Homecoming)

2
00:02:07,033 --> 00:02:08,400
(Episode 2)

3
00:02:11,633 --> 00:02:14,733
(Haoyunlai Inn)

4
00:02:18,966 --> 00:02:19,833
Welcome.

5
00:02:20,066 --> 00:02:21,500
What can I do for you?

6
00:02:22,533 --> 00:02:23,433
We are going to the city.

7
00:02:24,766 --> 00:02:27,066
So we need a comfortable
and reasonably priced pet as a mount.

8
00:02:29,700 --> 00:02:30,400
No problem.

9
00:02:30,866 --> 00:02:32,433
Please wait outside for a while.

10
00:02:33,933 --> 00:02:34,833
Greetings.

11
00:02:35,666 --> 00:02:36,233
Greetings, Mister.

12
00:02:37,033 --> 00:02:38,366
Please give me a pet of speed type.

13
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:39,300
I mean the speediest one.

14
00:02:40,900 --> 00:02:41,700
I'm from the Lingxiao Pavilion

15
00:02:41,933 --> 00:02:43,233
and we have an agreement membership of your post.

16
00:02:43,700 --> 00:02:44,766
No problem.

17
00:02:45,233 --> 00:02:46,333
Right away.

18
00:02:48,433 --> 00:02:49,166
Well.

19
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:51,866
Could you show me your sect code?

20
00:02:52,166 --> 00:02:53,366
Including moves and words.

21
00:03:02,133 --> 00:03:04,266
A little catfish, pa-pa.

22
00:03:04,700 --> 00:03:06,700
A big whale, wa-wa.

23
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,600
The Lingxiao Pavilion.

24
00:03:09,033 --> 00:03:10,833
MUA.

25
00:03:12,466 --> 00:03:13,200
What is that expression?

26
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:14,400
You've got a problem?

27
00:03:15,433 --> 00:03:16,033
Not at all.

28
00:03:16,166 --> 00:03:17,433
I'm checking it out.

29
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:20,900
- But I haven't found it. - I shouldn't have let Gu Ling...

30
00:03:20,900 --> 00:03:22,433
- Did you use the wrong code? - set the sect code.

31
00:03:22,466 --> 00:03:23,200
It's too embarrassing.

32
00:03:23,633 --> 00:03:25,133
Why don't you do it again?

33
00:03:25,466 --> 00:03:26,200
You wish.

34
00:03:30,933 --> 00:03:31,833
I've found it, Master.

35
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,300
It is the Lingxiao Pavilion's code.

36
00:03:33,966 --> 00:03:34,800
Then we are good.

37
00:03:35,233 --> 00:03:36,766
Give me a Sonic Falcon

38
00:03:37,066 --> 00:03:37,700
or a Shadow Panther.

39
00:03:38,666 --> 00:03:39,333
Master.

40
00:03:39,900 --> 00:03:41,166
But your sect

41
00:03:41,966 --> 00:03:42,833
has been

42
00:03:42,866 --> 00:03:44,233
removed from the list.

43
00:03:55,066 --> 00:03:56,300
Get out of the way!

44
00:04:11,466 --> 00:04:12,900
(Class Record: October of Year Jiachen)
In October of the Year Jiachen,

45
00:04:13,266 --> 00:04:14,933
(Succeeded in the sect challenge. Promoted to B-class.)
it succeeded in the sect challenge

46
00:04:15,166 --> 00:04:17,066
and was promoted to B-class.

47
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,233
In May of the Year Yisi,

48
00:04:19,666 --> 00:04:21,533
due to the accidental death of its master,

49
00:04:21,633 --> 00:04:23,700
(Degraded to C-class.)
it was degraded to C-class.

50
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,600
(August of Year Yisi)
In August of the Year Yisi,

51
00:04:26,033 --> 00:04:28,333
(The League issued the annihilation order on catfish.)
the League issued the annihilation order on catfish

52
00:04:28,866 --> 00:04:32,300
and wiped out all the pets
with hidden dangers in the Lingxiao Pavilion.

53
00:04:32,666 --> 00:04:34,433
(Degraded to D-class.)
It was degraded to D-class.

54
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,766
In February of the Year Bingwu,

55
00:04:37,133 --> 00:04:39,766
having been robbed of many resources by mass sects,

56
00:04:40,133 --> 00:04:41,933
the Lingxiao Pavilion suffered great losses.

57
00:04:42,533 --> 00:04:43,966
It was removed from the League list

58
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:46,033
and became a folk organization.

59
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:18,800
Hey.

60
00:05:19,533 --> 00:05:20,066
Look.

61
00:05:20,733 --> 00:05:21,533
What are you doing?

62
00:05:21,933 --> 00:05:22,466
Cooking.

63
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,900
Why did you make so many good dishes?

64
00:05:25,266 --> 00:05:26,500
Don't you know the situation

65
00:05:26,533 --> 00:05:27,400
of the Lingxiao Pavilion now?

66
00:05:27,866 --> 00:05:29,200
I'm so sorry.

67
00:05:29,466 --> 00:05:30,733
Even I don't know why.

68
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:32,033
I just feel

69
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:34,000
that we will have an important guest today.

70
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:38,400
(Spiritual Pet Service)

71
00:05:40,933 --> 00:05:41,833
Welcome.

72
00:05:44,666 --> 00:05:46,100
What can I do for you?

73
00:05:47,666 --> 00:05:49,333
My two pets are seriously wounded.

74
00:05:49,400 --> 00:05:50,600
They need emergency treatment.

75
00:05:53,933 --> 00:05:54,500
One more thing,

76
00:05:54,833 --> 00:05:55,300
could you

77
00:05:55,333 --> 00:05:57,000
issue status certificates for them?

78
00:05:58,166 --> 00:05:59,833
No problem. I'll take care of them.

79
00:06:01,933 --> 00:06:08,033
(Medicine)

80
00:06:08,866 --> 00:06:11,233
Do you have defense skill bubbles?

81
00:06:11,900 --> 00:06:12,333
Hold on.

82
00:06:12,700 --> 00:06:13,566
Let me look for it.

83
00:06:15,300 --> 00:06:16,633
(Account Book)

84
00:06:16,666 --> 00:06:17,233
Yes.

85
00:06:17,466 --> 00:06:18,400
There is only one left.

86
00:06:19,966 --> 00:06:20,666
Great.

87
00:06:21,233 --> 00:06:22,833
Things are getting smooth a bit.

88
00:06:24,166 --> 00:06:24,766
Wait.

89
00:06:25,433 --> 00:06:26,866
The last volume of bubbles

90
00:06:27,166 --> 00:06:27,933
is mine.

91
00:06:28,733 --> 00:06:30,566
I'll pay you three times the price.

92
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:33,866
So, storekeeper?

93
00:06:36,266 --> 00:06:36,966
Sorry.

94
00:06:37,466 --> 00:06:38,233
The last volume

95
00:06:38,566 --> 00:06:39,833
is bought by this customer.

96
00:06:40,333 --> 00:06:41,033
Yes.

97
00:06:41,433 --> 00:06:43,000
First come, first served.

98
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:45,300
Storekeeper.

99
00:06:46,033 --> 00:06:47,700
It's a shame

100
00:06:47,766 --> 00:06:49,000
to give up a large profit.

101
00:06:50,166 --> 00:06:52,066
If I, Xue Dashuai, want something,

102
00:06:52,166 --> 00:06:53,666
I must get it.

103
00:06:56,566 --> 00:06:57,433
Wait.

104
00:07:06,833 --> 00:07:07,766
Mister Liu?

105
00:07:13,133 --> 00:07:14,833
Whoa, Mister Liu.

106
00:07:14,866 --> 00:07:15,766
Take your time.

107
00:07:15,766 --> 00:07:17,000
How long haven't you eaten?

108
00:07:17,700 --> 00:07:18,533
Where have you been?

109
00:07:20,766 --> 00:07:21,600
Nowhere.

110
00:07:22,566 --> 00:07:24,500
I just grew flowers and raised dogs at home.

111
00:07:31,166 --> 00:07:32,266
Well...

112
00:07:36,100 --> 00:07:38,800
Mister Xue, I'd like to ask a favor.

113
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:41,866
Mister Liu.

114
00:07:42,433 --> 00:07:44,633
Something is not right with you.

115
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:47,900
How so?

116
00:07:48,266 --> 00:07:50,333
Why don't you drink alcohol today?

117
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,800
I drank too much with a girl last night.

118
00:07:55,333 --> 00:07:55,933
I don't care.

119
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:57,966
We need to have a good drink today.

120
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,500
If you drink me under the table,

121
00:07:59,633 --> 00:08:01,500
you can take anything from me.

122
00:08:01,700 --> 00:08:02,100
So?

123
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:07,700
All right then.

124
00:08:11,100 --> 00:08:11,666
Today

125
00:08:11,833 --> 00:08:13,766
is the first anniversary of the Lingxiao Pavilion.

126
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,500
(Lingxiao Pavilion)

127
00:08:14,533 --> 00:08:15,733
Thanks for your support.

128
00:08:16,466 --> 00:08:17,566
Let me drink first to show my respect.

129
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:26,500
The Lingxiao Pavilion, MUA.

130
00:08:30,166 --> 00:08:31,433
He has just drunk one cup of it.

131
00:08:36,033 --> 00:08:36,700
I can drink no more.

132
00:08:37,133 --> 00:08:39,000
You can drink like a fish, Mister Liu.

133
00:08:40,700 --> 00:08:42,266
To think I feel nothing at all.

134
00:08:43,166 --> 00:08:45,033
Liu Fengmang is such a heavy drinker.

135
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:51,600
Until next time, Mister Xue.

136
00:08:52,166 --> 00:08:54,000
I'm taking the bubble.

137
00:08:54,766 --> 00:08:56,433
No problem. Take all that you want.

138
00:09:06,733 --> 00:09:07,366
Don't be afraid.

139
00:09:08,566 --> 00:09:09,933
Let me untie you now.

140
00:09:11,366 --> 00:09:13,600
Don't be caught by those guys again.

141
00:09:25,300 --> 00:09:26,133
Nian.

142
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,733
Though you have learned Bubble,

143
00:09:29,133 --> 00:09:30,166
it's just the beginning.

144
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:31,800
Now,

145
00:09:32,233 --> 00:09:33,533
let's go see our old friends.

146
00:09:45,700 --> 00:09:46,933
Duan Ye.

147
00:09:49,066 --> 00:09:50,433
Some...

148
00:09:51,066 --> 00:09:51,900
Some people came here.

149
00:09:58,800 --> 00:10:00,066
Who dares challenge our Lingxiao Pavilion?

150
00:10:01,800 --> 00:10:03,100
It's such a waste

151
00:10:03,366 --> 00:10:05,300
(Mega Rock Gang)
to let a useless sect

152
00:10:05,700 --> 00:10:06,966
use this good place.

153
00:10:07,766 --> 00:10:10,366
Pack up and get lost if you want to live.

154
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:12,933
This place belongs to our Mega Rock Gang now.

155
00:10:15,766 --> 00:10:17,200
Even a rabble

156
00:10:17,466 --> 00:10:18,933
dare break into here?

157
00:10:19,333 --> 00:10:20,733
That's so annoying.

158
00:10:22,733 --> 00:10:23,800
It's a speed type.

159
00:10:24,100 --> 00:10:24,800
Corner it.

160
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:25,300
Yes.

161
00:10:33,300 --> 00:10:34,500
My Gravel Turtle.

162
00:10:52,566 --> 00:10:53,266
Unicorn Beetle.

163
00:10:56,433 --> 00:10:58,100
(Shade Feline
The third phase of the Soul-building Stage)

164
00:10:58,566 --> 00:11:01,166
You scums dare have designs on our pavilion.

165
00:11:01,666 --> 00:11:02,966
So unwise.

166
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:06,700
You must have some misunderstandings about Shade Feline.

167
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:09,400
What makes you think you gnats

168
00:11:09,466 --> 00:11:11,800
can rampage at our place?

169
00:11:12,666 --> 00:11:14,200
You are just wasting my time.

170
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,033
Don't you know

171
00:11:16,166 --> 00:11:18,166
the Lingxiao Pavilion is the strongest?

172
00:11:19,133 --> 00:11:20,433
Why are you still standing there?

173
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:21,833
Show me

174
00:11:22,033 --> 00:11:23,333
what else you can do.

175
00:11:24,066 --> 00:11:25,000
Don't let me...

176
00:11:37,033 --> 00:11:37,666
Look out.

177
00:11:41,933 --> 00:11:42,933
Heimi.

178
00:11:49,900 --> 00:11:52,200
(The All-devouring Whale)

179
00:11:52,700 --> 00:11:54,733
The Lingxiao Pavilion, I'm back.

180
00:11:58,400 --> 00:12:00,600
I wonder what they are doing now.

181
00:12:05,700 --> 00:12:07,033
How did it become this

182
00:12:07,433 --> 00:12:08,600
within a mere year?

183
00:12:12,233 --> 00:12:14,133
(Lingxiao Pavilion)

184
00:12:16,833 --> 00:12:17,800
Where are the caretakers?

185
00:12:18,700 --> 00:12:20,366
The gate is open. What are they...?

186
00:12:21,100 --> 00:12:21,933
What happened?

187
00:12:33,233 --> 00:12:34,066
Heimi.

188
00:12:34,933 --> 00:12:35,933
Heimi.

189
00:12:39,866 --> 00:12:40,833
Mister Duan.

190
00:12:45,866 --> 00:12:46,666
Mister Duan.

191
00:12:52,566 --> 00:12:53,233
Heimi.

192
00:12:56,566 --> 00:12:57,266
No.

193
00:12:58,566 --> 00:13:00,033
Don't leave me.

194
00:13:04,366 --> 00:13:05,100
Heimi.

195
00:13:08,966 --> 00:13:09,700
Don't go.

196
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:11,433
Don't.

197
00:13:26,566 --> 00:13:29,366
Your Lingxiao Pavilion is just a folk organization.

198
00:13:30,533 --> 00:13:31,500
Now

199
00:13:31,633 --> 00:13:33,933
you don't even have a pet to fight.

200
00:13:36,700 --> 00:13:38,800
So you'd better give this place to us.

201
00:13:40,766 --> 00:13:41,966
Otherwise...

202
00:13:45,166 --> 00:13:45,966
What is that?

203
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:51,633
Where is that pup from?

204
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:53,100
That's my line.

205
00:13:54,500 --> 00:13:56,033
Where are you from, scums?

206
00:13:59,733 --> 00:14:01,466
How dare you offend our Lingxiao Pavilion?

207
00:14:01,933 --> 00:14:03,800
Don't be a busybody, rascal.

208
00:14:04,033 --> 00:14:05,933
I will bury you with them.

209
00:14:06,300 --> 00:14:07,200
Busybody?

210
00:14:07,733 --> 00:14:09,066
This is my turf in the first place.

211
00:14:10,133 --> 00:14:11,366
Silver, go.

212
00:14:13,366 --> 00:14:15,066
Have you lost your mind?

213
00:14:15,166 --> 00:14:16,766
Using a stupid pup to face me?

214
00:14:17,166 --> 00:14:18,300
Dragon Lizard.

215
00:14:26,866 --> 00:14:27,566
What?

216
00:14:28,133 --> 00:14:30,833
It blocked Dragon Lizard's claw unscathed?

217
00:14:31,566 --> 00:14:32,400
Too weak.

218
00:14:32,666 --> 00:14:33,400
Teddy.

219
00:14:33,733 --> 00:14:34,466
The ultimate skill.

220
00:14:46,300 --> 00:14:47,100
Nonsense.

221
00:14:47,333 --> 00:14:48,533
A stupid pup

222
00:14:48,566 --> 00:14:50,266
could defeat my Dragon Lizard?

223
00:14:50,566 --> 00:14:51,200
How is that possible?

224
00:14:53,566 --> 00:14:55,633
Those guys are too green.

225
00:14:55,866 --> 00:14:58,166
It was influenced by Teddy's Feeble Urine,

226
00:14:58,200 --> 00:14:59,100
but they didn't notice it.

227
00:15:00,166 --> 00:15:01,400
That's why they are defeated.

228
00:15:02,633 --> 00:15:03,600
Don't be afraid, boys.

229
00:15:03,933 --> 00:15:05,566
Summon all your backup pets.

230
00:15:06,100 --> 00:15:07,166
He's just alone

231
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:09,233
and is outnumbered.

232
00:15:10,300 --> 00:15:11,100
Forget that dog

233
00:15:11,233 --> 00:15:12,533
and attack its master.

234
00:15:15,566 --> 00:15:16,400
That's too mean.

235
00:15:16,666 --> 00:15:18,400
How dare you use pets to attack an ordinary man?

236
00:15:20,733 --> 00:15:21,766
I'll be so dead

237
00:15:21,800 --> 00:15:23,000
if I don't get away.

238
00:15:27,800 --> 00:15:29,966
Boss, it works.

239
00:15:30,066 --> 00:15:31,066
Eradicate him.

240
00:15:31,266 --> 00:15:32,800
We shall never let that guy run away.

241
00:15:36,700 --> 00:15:37,400
Where?

242
00:15:37,766 --> 00:15:38,600
Where is he?

243
00:15:39,700 --> 00:15:40,133
Boss.

244
00:15:43,700 --> 00:15:44,366
Nian.

245
00:15:44,700 --> 00:15:45,666
Thank them for their food.

246
00:15:46,333 --> 00:15:46,900
That is...

247
00:15:47,333 --> 00:15:48,133
A whale!

248
00:15:48,400 --> 00:15:51,133
I was wondering where to find so many high-quality pets.

249
00:15:53,066 --> 00:15:55,300
Didn't the League issue the order to eliminate catfishes?

250
00:15:55,433 --> 00:15:57,133
How do you have one?

251
00:15:57,166 --> 00:15:58,466
I... I will expose it.

252
00:16:00,700 --> 00:16:02,400
Nobody will know it

253
00:16:02,566 --> 00:16:04,266
if it devours you all.

254
00:16:05,800 --> 00:16:07,300
I'll let you go this time.

255
00:16:07,300 --> 00:16:08,866
Wh-when I see you again,

256
00:16:08,900 --> 00:16:10,100
I'll make you pay.

257
00:16:10,133 --> 00:16:11,900
That's right.

258
00:16:11,900 --> 00:16:13,633
Boss, wait for us.

259
00:16:17,533 --> 00:16:19,266
Even their checking out was so inferior.

260
00:16:23,366 --> 00:16:24,100
Hero.

261
00:16:27,566 --> 00:16:28,266
Hero.

262
00:16:30,533 --> 00:16:31,633
Thank you for your help.

263
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:34,700
When we were in great trouble, thanks to...

264
00:16:40,566 --> 00:16:41,566
It's great

265
00:16:43,900 --> 00:16:44,700
to see you again.

266
00:16:49,466 --> 00:16:51,733
He... Hero?

267
00:16:53,966 --> 00:16:55,966
Who... Who are you?

268
00:16:58,800 --> 00:16:59,700
Can't recognize me?

269
00:16:59,933 --> 00:17:00,533
I am...

270
00:17:01,733 --> 00:17:02,300
Wait.

271
00:17:02,666 --> 00:17:03,733
I can't tell her now.

272
00:17:04,433 --> 00:17:05,900
The Black Whale must have turned into the Corpse Whale

273
00:17:06,433 --> 00:17:07,833
because of someone's scheme.

274
00:17:08,033 --> 00:17:08,633
It could even

275
00:17:09,100 --> 00:17:10,300
be my most familiar person.

276
00:17:10,300 --> 00:17:10,933
Hero?

277
00:17:13,800 --> 00:17:14,900
The name is Liu Fengmang.

278
00:17:15,066 --> 00:17:17,300
You are just like an old friend to me.

279
00:17:18,333 --> 00:17:19,166
I am Gu Ling.

280
00:17:19,433 --> 00:17:21,466
I thank you on behalf of my people.

281
00:17:25,666 --> 00:17:26,166
Gu Ling.

282
00:17:26,966 --> 00:17:28,766
Let's go check on the others.

283
00:17:43,666 --> 00:17:45,166
Hero, a moment, please.

284
00:17:47,200 --> 00:17:47,633
Everyone.

285
00:17:48,066 --> 00:17:49,800
This is Mister Liu who helped us.

286
00:17:51,666 --> 00:17:53,266
You are welcome. It's my duty.

287
00:18:01,300 --> 00:18:03,366
Miss Gu, you need to see Mister Duan.

288
00:18:07,233 --> 00:18:07,900
Mister Duan.

289
00:18:08,933 --> 00:18:09,866
How are you holding up?

290
00:18:23,433 --> 00:18:24,233
I've caught it at last.

291
00:18:25,366 --> 00:18:26,166
This Shade Feline

292
00:18:26,366 --> 00:18:27,700
is a rare one.

293
00:18:28,266 --> 00:18:29,033
Congratulations, Master.

294
00:18:37,433 --> 00:18:38,566
It likes you.

295
00:18:38,933 --> 00:18:40,000
So why don't you keep it?

296
00:18:41,800 --> 00:18:42,333
Really?

297
00:18:43,433 --> 00:18:44,600
Don't you like it?

298
00:18:45,266 --> 00:18:46,966
Cultivate it well.

299
00:18:48,033 --> 00:18:48,933
Trust me, Master.

300
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:50,766
I will never desert it

301
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:52,966
and make it the strongest pet.

302
00:18:56,033 --> 00:18:56,900
I'm going.

303
00:18:59,533 --> 00:19:00,233
Going?

304
00:19:00,633 --> 00:19:01,433
To where?

305
00:19:02,066 --> 00:19:03,266
I'm leaving the Lingxiao Pavilion.

306
00:19:05,300 --> 00:19:06,066
What did you say?

307
00:19:07,266 --> 00:19:08,800
All of our spiritual pets are dead.

308
00:19:09,733 --> 00:19:11,566
There is no need to go back to the Lingxiao Pavilion.

309
00:19:12,500 --> 00:19:14,733
So it's pointless to stay here.

310
00:19:22,100 --> 00:19:23,633
This is the Lingxiao Pavilion.

311
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,433
How could there be nothing?

312
00:19:26,766 --> 00:19:27,633
It's just you?

313
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:28,866
Yes.

314
00:19:29,500 --> 00:19:30,533
I am the master of the Lingxiao Pavilion.

315
00:19:32,900 --> 00:19:34,533
You've become a master so young?

316
00:19:34,866 --> 00:19:36,200
Can you do it?

317
00:19:37,100 --> 00:19:38,800
There is not even a plaque above the gate.

318
00:19:38,933 --> 00:19:40,600
Yet you still want to be the top one?

319
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:42,300
Seriously?

320
00:19:47,566 --> 00:19:48,133
Don't go.

321
00:19:51,166 --> 00:19:52,266
There is still hope for the Lingxiao Pavilion.

322
00:19:52,700 --> 00:19:54,233
I can help you rebuild...

323
00:20:00,866 --> 00:20:02,466
Who do you think you are?

324
00:20:04,300 --> 00:20:07,000
Does our Pavilion need the pity of you, a stranger?

325
00:20:07,133 --> 00:20:08,100
Listen up.

326
00:20:08,233 --> 00:20:10,266
Our Lingxiao Pavilion is the strongest.

327
00:20:10,433 --> 00:20:12,766
Your abilities are nothing.

328
00:20:15,366 --> 00:20:16,100
I mean it.

329
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:23,033
I'm going to build a top sect.

330
00:20:26,433 --> 00:20:27,866
Sounds like true.

331
00:20:30,033 --> 00:20:31,200
Don't let me down.

332
00:20:42,266 --> 00:20:43,066
Mister Duan.

333
00:20:45,300 --> 00:20:47,166
You can't leave.

334
00:20:48,166 --> 00:20:50,033
We need to carry on Master's will

335
00:20:50,666 --> 00:20:51,966
and protect the Pavilion.

336
00:20:52,600 --> 00:20:54,200
But Master is dead.

337
00:20:56,666 --> 00:20:57,600
Lingxiao Pavilion

338
00:20:58,433 --> 00:21:00,200
was supported by him alone.

339
00:21:01,500 --> 00:21:02,300
Without him,

340
00:21:02,600 --> 00:21:04,033
we are nothing.

341
00:21:05,433 --> 00:21:07,000
Duan Ye, you fool.

342
00:21:07,600 --> 00:21:08,933
Don't say that.

343
00:21:09,666 --> 00:21:10,633
We can still...

344
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:12,100
Just face the reality.

345
00:21:12,566 --> 00:21:14,700
The Pavilion died one year ago.

346
00:21:20,633 --> 00:21:21,466
Sorry.

347
00:21:22,633 --> 00:21:23,700
I'm leaving here

348
00:21:24,400 --> 00:21:25,533
to start over.

349
00:21:25,566 --> 00:21:28,300
(The All-devouring Whale)

350
00:21:30,700 --> 00:21:32,033
Wu. Li Zhou.

351
00:21:32,566 --> 00:21:33,933
Please talk to Duan Ye.

352
00:21:36,600 --> 00:21:37,933
Sorry, Miss Gu.

353
00:21:38,800 --> 00:21:40,633
The Lingxiao Pavilion exists in name only.

354
00:21:41,100 --> 00:21:42,366
Soon its name is going to perish.

355
00:21:42,800 --> 00:21:44,466
Thank you for taking care of us so far.

356
00:21:47,300 --> 00:21:48,333
Take care of yourself.

357
00:21:53,966 --> 00:21:54,733
Don't go.

358
00:21:54,866 --> 00:21:56,333
The Pavilion still exists.

359
00:21:59,033 --> 00:22:00,133
Mister Duan.

360
00:22:31,533 --> 00:22:32,733
(Lingxiao Pavilion)
Dear Lingxiao Pavilion.

361
00:22:35,266 --> 00:22:36,066
May you

362
00:22:37,800 --> 00:22:38,966
be well.

363
00:22:39,166 --> 00:22:42,166
(Lingxiao Pavilion)

364
00:22:48,866 --> 00:22:49,833
Please

365
00:22:50,333 --> 00:22:51,533
give me some time.

366
00:22:53,433 --> 00:22:55,600
I'll take care of all the problems

367
00:22:56,233 --> 00:22:58,666
and bring the Pavilion back on the right track.

368
00:22:59,733 --> 00:23:00,366
So...

369
00:23:01,200 --> 00:23:01,766
So...

370
00:23:02,266 --> 00:23:03,133
Don't go.

371
00:23:04,166 --> 00:23:05,333
Please stay.

372
00:23:08,900 --> 00:23:12,766
♪Ask not about tears♪
(Lingxiao Pavilion)

373
00:23:12,900 --> 00:23:18,900
♪The soul is broken and the dream is shattered quietly♪

374
00:25:10,966 --> 00:25:12,266
I will join the Lingxiao Pavilion.

375
00:25:15,166 --> 00:25:16,100
I swear

376
00:25:17,533 --> 00:25:18,666
I will bring the Lingxiao Pavilion

377
00:25:19,700 --> 00:25:21,066
back to the peak.